Case Study 24: Expense Tracker
Problem Statement
Individuals want to monitor and categorize their spending habits. This project focuses on
designing and developing a Flutter-based mobile application related to 'Expense Tracker'.
Students are expected to understand the real-world problem, analyze user requirements, and
design an intuitive mobile interface. The application should demonstrate how mobile technology
can simplify everyday tasks and improve user experience through efficient design and
functionality.
Detailed Feature List
Charts using Flutter chart packages, SQL database, Form validation for expense
entries, DateTime pickers, Stateful widgets for financial summaries, JSON export for
reports.
Expected Outcome
Create a spending tracker that records transactions and analyzes expense patterns.